		<tr><td>Message</td><td>$message</td></tr>
		</table></body></html>";
		
		$headers = 'Content-type: text/html; charset=iso-8859-1' . "\r\n".'From: contact@anandapurnirgariberasha.org' . "\r\n\n" .
